Sort Words in a Sentence | Sort words in a sentence alphabetically. |

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog";
        System.out.println("sort words in a string: "+ sortWords(str));
    }
    public static String sortWords(String str){
        
        String[] words = str.split(" ");            // Split the sentence into words
        
        Arrays.sort(words);                        // Sort the words in alphabetical order
        
        return String.join(" ",words);             // Join the sorted words back into a single string
    }
}

output:
sort words in a string: The brown dog fox jumps lazy over quick the
